sequenceDiagram
    participant U as Người dùng
    participant AO as AgentOrchestrator
    participant LP as AgentLoop
    participant CG as CitationGuard
    U->>AO: stream_answer(question)
    AO->>LP: run() — non-stream
    LP-->>AO: Final Answer + structured_trace
    AO-->>U: event 'step' (Đang tra cứu...)
    Note over AO,CG: verify TRƯỚC khi stream token
    AO->>CG: check(final, trace)
    CG-->>AO: GuardResult (verify/repair/annotate)
    AO-->>U: event 'meta' (nguồn, sau verify)
    AO-->>U: event 'token' × N (đã verify, _chunk_text)
    AO-->>U: event 'done'
